---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Cofoundy">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-white">
    <Navbar />
    <main class="pt-32 pb-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-secondary mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: December 2025</p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p>By accessing and using Cofoundy's services, you agree to these terms of service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you may not use our services.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
            <p>Cofoundy is a software consultancy that offers:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Web and application development</li>
              <li>Artificial intelligence solutions</li>
              <li>MVP development for startups</li>
              <li>Technology consulting</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4">3. Client Obligations</h2>
            <p>By contracting our services, you agree to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Provide accurate and up-to-date information</li>
              <li>Make agreed payments within established deadlines</li>
              <li>Collaborate in defining project requirements</li>
              <li>Respect intellectual property rights</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>Upon full payment of the project, the client receives usage rights to the developed software. Cofoundy retains the right to use generic components and methodologies in other projects.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>Cofoundy shall not be liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services or products.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4">6. Modifications</h2>
            <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will take effect immediately upon publication on this site.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
            <p>For inquiries about these terms, contact us at:</p>
            <p class="mt-2">
              <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@cofoundy.dev" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@cofoundy.dev</a>
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
